headline: Stryker announces Annual Meeting of Shareholders
summary: Portage, Michigan, March 25, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Stryker (NYSE:SYK) announced its 2025 Annual Meeting of Shareholders is scheduled as follows: Thursday, May 8, 2025 – 9:30 a.m. Eastern Time The Meeting will be held virtually via the internet. Information about the webcast, which will include both the audio and the slide presentation from the meeting, is available on the Investor Relations page of our website at www.investorevents.stryker.com. To listen to the meeting as a guest dial (877) 3
